{"1": {"comment_id": "nishmakespizza"  "comment_text": "75% whole wheat.

Formula:
* 360g levain (80% hydration)
* 710g @bartonspringsmill Rouge de Bourdeaux
* 90g @kingarthurbaking Sir Galahad
* 660g water
* 21g salt
* 1.75g instant yeast

Method:
* Bake @ 400f with steam for 20 mins
* Remove steam  vent  bake for another 30 mins to internal temp of 205f
* Remove from pans  bake for another 5 mins to create crust

Yield: two loaves (5x9)

Adapted from @maurizio and @kenforkish

main_text: I grew some wheat over the winter indoors in a bucket of recycled soil I found on the side of the road by sewing bird seed into it by accident.So I am growing more of it indoors and outdoors.By the looks of the world right now growing your own wheat is probably going to become a pretty popular past time; especially once we run out of gas completely or summer temperatures kill too many people to sustain society or the machinery breaks down.We took the wrong technology path and now we are becoming useless digital zombies.Given how automation of jobs has gone in the past I also dont expect some robot slave utopia where money is obsolete and we all live happy lives with all the time in the world for VR porn.So if I become one of the 100s of millions of roaming homeless I can at least find a remote location to start a stealth farm on Crown Land.#wheat #society #civilization #gardening #meditations #endoftheworldtour
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "reflectionfrequency"  "comment_text": "I grew some wheat over the winter indoors in a bucket of recycled soil I found on the side of the road by sewing bird seed into it by accident.

So I am growing more of it indoors and outdoors.

By the looks of the world right now  growing your own wheat is probably going to become a pretty popular past time; especially once we run out of gas completely or summer temperatures kill too many people to sustain society or the machinery breaks down.

We took the wrong technology path and now we are becoming useless digital zombies.

Given how automation of jobs has gone in the past I also dont expect some robot slave utopia where money is obsolete and we all live happy lives with all the time in the world for VR porn.

So if I become one of the 100s of millions of roaming homeless I can at least find a remote location to start a stealth farm on Crown Land.

#wheat #society #civilization #gardening #meditations #endoftheworldtour"}}
